The evidence with the title 'State Of Oregon: employers - contribution rates ' says Employer contribution rates change every other odd year (i.e.: 2017, 2019, 2021).  ... These rates were adopted by the PERS Board on october 5 , 2018, and are final .  ... There are currently three types of contributions : member paid pre-tax ( mppt)  ... OPSRP ) , into which employers contribute a percentage of employee salary. 
